      "en": "Al-Kafirun is beautifully constructed: قُلْ (verbal), لَا أَعْبُدُ (verbal), وَلَا أَنْتُمْ عَابِدُونَ (verbal — عَابِدُونَ is a participle used as a verb), but وَلَكُمْ دِينُكُمْ (nominal — no verb). The surah deliberately contrasts the two sentence types.",
